==赤式和苏式==
有机化学的习惯命名法中，使用“苏”或“苏式”（"threo"）表示相邻两碳相同官能团在费歇尔投影式中处于异侧的构型。<ref name="Rausch">[http://www2.chemistry.msu.edu:80/faculty/reusch/VirtTxtJml/sterism3.htm#isom17b Formulas Using Other Configurational Notations] {{Wayback|url=http://www2.chemistry.msu.edu/faculty/reusch/VirtTxtJml/sterism3.htm#isom17b |date=20210503152817 }}, W. Rausch, accessed 1 March 2011</ref>这种命名源自苏糖的构型。相对的，两个官能团在同侧的为赤式构型（"erythro"）。<ref name="Rausch"/><ref>Prof. Rausch helpfully notes that the prefixes "may be applied to racemic compounds, as well as pure enantiomers and meso compounds", and that when depicted in the common "zig-zag" representation, adjacent "substituents may lie on the same side of the carbon chain... [syn] or on opposite sides... [anti]", which is opposite of their depiction in a [[Fischer_projection|Fischer projection]].</ref>赤式和苏式为[[差向异构体|差向异构体]]。

